    "nom_orig": "Sister[SP]#2",
    "texte_orig": "There's[SP]no[SP]point[SP]cowering[SP]in[SP]fear.[1205][U+000F][SP]I[SP]mean,\nwho'd[SP]waste[SP]their[SP]time[SP]bombing[SP]a[SP]drugstore?",
